---
// Join the Journey section - Transparency about being early stage
---

<section id="join-journey" class="py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-black">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#d4ff2a]/10 to-green-400/10 border border-[#d4ff2a]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <!-- Icon -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-[#d4ff2a]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#d4ff2a]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Heading -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
        We're Just Getting Started
      </h2>

      <!-- Message -->
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        hilm.ai is a new product, and we're building it in the open. If you're reading this, you're among the early users who will help shape what hilm.ai becomes.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your feedback, your questions, and your needs will directly influence the product's direction. Be a founding member and help us build something truly useful.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://t.me/hilmaibot"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-[#d4ff2a] text-black font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-[#c5f01a] transform hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-[#d4ff2a]/20"
        >
          <span>Try It Now</span>
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://t.me/omark4y"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="px-8 py-4 bg-gray-800/50 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-800 hover:border-[#d4ff2a]/50 transition-all backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
          Share Feedback
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

